snippet.title: Best VGM 2280 - Professor Layton and the Curious Village - Puzzle
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 271 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j_8sYSOkwAg

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Professor Layton and the Curious Village (2007)
Puzzle
Tomohito Nishiura
